response.original_title: The Great American Baking Show: Celebrity Holiday Special
response.overview: Six celebrities - Arturo Castro, DeAndre Jordan, Joel McHale, Heather McMahan, Ego Nwodim, Phoebe Robinson - join The Great American Baking Show judges Paul Hollywood and Prue Leith in the iconic tent. With holiday humor they whisk, bake, and fake their way through three challenges
response.title: The Great American Baking Show: Celebrity Holiday Special
